  • Type Parameters:
    V - the MVP IBaseContract.IView interface this presenter gets connected to.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBaseContract.IPresenter<V>, IBaseContract.IPresenterLifecycle<V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AccountAddPresenter, AccountEditPresenter, AListActivityPresenter, CategoryAddPresenter, CategoryEditPresenter, ChartActivityPresenter, ReportFormPresenter, TransactionAddPresenter, TransactionEditPresenter
    public abstract class ABasePresenter<V extends IBaseContract.IView>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBaseContract.IPresenter<V>
    An abstract implementation of the presenter base interface IBaseContract.IPresenter providing basic functionality to store the view and clean up the reference on view destruction.

    Further it stores the viewState as an observable, which can be used with the ChangingDataWithViewState decorator for the ChangingData interface. This allows stopping notifying ChangingData.Observer if the view is not visible and also removes all observers if the view gets destroyed to prevent leaks.
